service will be held at 5:30 p.m. Saturday, Feb. 29, in the UVA Chapel. Following the service, friends and family members are invited to gather in the auditorium of the University\u2019s Harrison Institute and Small Special Collections Library, 160 McCormick Road.</p></div><div class=\"_3x-2\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;H&quot;}\"><div data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;H&quot;}\"><div class=\"mtm\"><div id=\"u_0_16\" class=\"_6m2 _1zpr clearfix _dcs _4_w4 _5cwb _23bq _2bf7 _64lx _3eqz _20pq _3eqw _2rk1\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;H&quot;}\"><div class=\"clearfix _2r3x\"><div class=\"lfloat _ohe\"><span class=\"_3m6-\"><div class=\"_6ks\"><a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fengineering.virginia.edu%2Fnews%2F2020%2F02%2Fmemoriam-professor-stephanie-guerlain&amp;h=AT0l6RpaBVN-ZwmAzE9FQXaWDaJtfwPQFhx7sQ9cNZH8mpSjgD6PRHIywlw5ZtOT0lwtKRceDK98n02IINZjKJujdv3pvzJdylMhl2VRYJgTb_uUgbSFD0wp0VaKkYmHQs14gmRYcpXxJoAfjkTq03qXtubu5T-Y1M1Hq4QGiFhbjwOTAoesTQVsK0JJY6sVgSxVe4VJfB8Jx2jGVG0ip-HHw41q-A3T8ErSRBHSvc_2l1EcRPZLKD6YPx3aMo70gqZjMPLaslWSnc2kLPninrbQuBdb1cfxJ1tI3LIKNE7mHuf0bIdEwlPDjklq3J1BiXZEOipQ2EUOjTiEg_NGXMiN1Yk4myeXOaiyHzaeszGxyJ9sK8d8QlN977-T8RVG7pVFCLZTt1OHwGiYQWizvZO6Fp_Ds5PIa7U_W0tWWFVagCenAxR_aF8tRBYjczFwYt5dSl8P6Hu3tl2E7OBgce7VK5Tx1PE5EOds1Mf-wYozlVh2CM0i7LJ0iALqRX3oIWFuSXJNGpoPlLCobS_aQipmvDntdDgz0X7E-IVLTAHeq2sRb4ED4UTkzprNVP7Ac6K4eqomn9fr1btaiP7e8SVi62z0WbYr7sPZOhRAVf09KkHR3X2ghLF-X3HD-csLb-_TPg6e7YbXAuQHh_ZXdb3a9nZfPm4W\" aria-describedby=\"u_0_1g\" aria-label=\"In Memoriam: Professor Stephanie A.
